This value set includes codes based on the following rules:

  • Import all the codes that are contained in http://terminology.hl7.org/ValueSet/v3-PermanentDentition
  • Import all the codes that are contained in http://terminology.hl7.org/ValueSet/v3-SupernumeraryTooth
  • Import all the codes that are contained in http://terminology.hl7.org/ValueSet/v3-PrimaryDentition
  • Import all the codes that are contained in http://terminology.hl7.org/ValueSet/v3-ArtificialDentition
  • Include all codes defined in http://terminology.hl7.org/CodeSystem/v3-Dentition
